> Windlord and Perceptor approached in silence and carefully watched

<NEW>

After landing the shuttle and comming back to watch the advanced
proto-humans, it easy to see that these humans are a little more
advanced. They have stone tools and weapons, and are all standing
around a large statue of some sort.

Slowly they start to chant and to walk around the statue, their voices
rising and falling in some strange language as they wave various
plants at the stone statue.

The statues themselves look like some sort of large insect, perhaps a
preting mantis or some other type of insect. In fact the statues
appear to be carved in the likeness of the PREDACON called BLIGHT!

The statue of BLIGHT looked to be farily well carved, includsing eye
holes and intriccatly careved mandibles. Then the eye holes began to
glow as its mandibles opened.

As this happned the proto humans stopped chanting as several members
robed in animal furs stepped foward and began to throw glowing rocks
into the madibles of the statue of BLIGHT!
